            // that matched /[*+-]|\d+[.]/ would just create the next <li>, causing this mismatch:
            //
            //  Markdown          rendered by WMD        rendered by MarkdownSharp
            //  ------------------------------------------------------------------
            //  1. first          1. first               1. first
            //  2. second         2. second              2. second
            //  - third           3. third                   * third
